OL,6,GChannel 4's fabulous new idents have
OL,7,Greceived a big thumbs up from many
OL,8,GPres fans.
OL,10,FBut if you've been keeping a close
OL,11,Feye ` or rather ear ` on things, you
OL,12,Fmay have noticed something a little
OL,13,Fmore concerning.
OL,15,FThe vast majority of continuity links
OL,16,Fbefore 7pm now appear to be very
OL,17,Fgeneric.
OL,19,FThe announcer simply plugs a
OL,20,Fprogramme later in the week or
OL,21,Fsomething available online over the
OL,22,Fident.
OL,3,CThe slippery slope of pre-recorded
OL,4,Ccontinuity announcements
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G1/6
