OL,6,FIf they are not fundamentally there
OL,7,Fas the live link between the viewer
OL,8,Fand the broadcaster, what is the
OL,9,Fpoint of them?
OL,11,FThe time could be spent on more
OL,12,Fpromotions or be used to accommodate
OL,13,Fextra advertising if Ofcom gives the
OL,14,Fgreen light to proposals to allow
OL,15,Fmore commercials on PSBs.
OL,17,FIt is not hard to mount an argument
OL,18,Fthat traditional announcers are no
OL,19,Flonger quite as fundamental to smooth
OL,20,Fpresentation as was once the case.
OL,3,CThe slippery slope of pre-recorded
OL,4,Ccontinuity announcements
