OL,6,FBreakdowns are rare and Channel 4
OL,7,Frarely has last-minute programme
OL,8,Fchanges.
OL,10,FBut this argument would be very short-
OL,11,Fsighted.
OL,13,FAt their best, announcers remind
OL,14,Fviewers that channels are living,
OL,15,Fbreathing, live services ` not the
OL,16,Fimpersonal robotic product of a
OL,17,Fserver loaded up hours earlier.
OL,3,CThe slippery slope of pre-recorded
OL,4,Ccontinuity announcements
