OL,6,FIn recent years it has become common
OL,7,Fto pre-record some links on major
OL,8,Fchannels ` even, sadly, on BBC One
OL,9,Fand Two. There is no continuity on
OL,10,FITV 1 until 1.30pm.
OL,12,FBut that does not mean this is
OL,13,Fdesirable.
OL,15,FSome BBC announcers, such as Duncan
OL,16,FNewmarch, are unsung heroes. His
OL,17,Fscripting on the night when Christmas
OL,18,Fwas effectively cancelled in December
OL,19,F2020 was appreciated by many.
OL,3,CThe slippery slope of pre-recorded
